nd the globe.\", \"from\": 5498, \"to\": 5563, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 5520, \"to\": 5522}, {\"ngram\": \"billions\", \"from\": 5527, \"to\": 5535}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5539, \"to\": 5545}, {\"ngram\": \"the globe\", \"from\": 5553, \"to\": 5562}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you for making us dream.\", \"from\": 5564, \"to\": 5594, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 5585, \"to\": 5587}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you for making us believe in a better world for everyone.\", \"from\": 5595, \"to\": 5658, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 5616, \"to\": 5618}, {\"ngram\": \"a better world\", \"from\": 5630, \"to\": 5644}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 5649, \"to\": 5657}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We know that the Olympic Games cannot create peace.\", \"from\": 5658, \"to\": 5710, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 5672, \"to\": 5689}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 5704, \"to\": 5709}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the Olympic Games can create a culture of peace that inspires the world.\", \"from\": 5711, \"to\": 5787, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 5715, \"to\": 5732}, {\"ngram\": \"a culture\", \"from\": 5744, \"to\": 5753}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 5757, \"to\": 5762}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 5777, \"to\": 5786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is why I call on everyone who shares this Olympic spirit: let us live this culture of peace every single day.\", \"from\": 5788, \"to\": 5902, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 5810, \"to\": 5818}, {\"ngram\": \"this Olympic spirit\", \"from\": 5830, \"to\": 5849}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 5855, \"to\": 5857}, {\"ngram\": \"this culture\", \"from\": 5863, \"to\": 5875}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 5879, \"to\": 5884}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There was also 