 stadium to collect the Olympic flag, before departing on a motorcycle to begin its journey across the AtlanticYee won the men's triathlon in dramatic fashion, while Page won Britain's first ever Olympic trampoline gold.Great Britain finished seventh in the medal table with 14 gold, 22 silver and 29 bronze.\", \"from\": 7057, \"to\": 7540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7088, \"end\": 7093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.556120703327853e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 7111, \"end\": 7119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alex Yee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\"}, {\"begin\": 7124, \"end\": 7135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryony_Page\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bryony Page\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryony_Page\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryony_Page\"}, {\"begin\": 7141, \"end\": 7154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9997172855690801, \"rank\": 0.00028061469584569014, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 7191, \"end\": 7201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}, {\"begin\": 7407, \"end\": 7414, \"title\": \"http://dbp