692}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 8696, \"to\": 8702}, {\"ngram\": \"the globe\", \"from\": 8710, \"to\": 8719}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you for making us dream.\", \"from\": 8721, \"to\": 8751, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 8742, \"to\": 8744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you for making us believe in a better world for everyone.\", \"from\": 8752, \"to\": 8815, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 8773, \"to\": 8775}, {\"ngram\": \"a better world\", \"from\": 8787, \"to\": 8801}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 8806, \"to\": 8814}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We know that the Olympic Games cannot create peace.\", \"from\": 8815, \"to\": 8867, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 8829, \"to\": 8846}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 8861, \"to\": 8866}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the Olympic Games can create a culture of peace that inspires the world.\", \"from\": 8868, \"to\": 8944, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 8872, \"to\": 8889}, {\"ngram\": \"a culture\", \"from\": 8901, \"to\": 8910}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 8914, \"to\": 8919}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 8934, \"to\": 8943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is why I call on everyone who shares this Olympic spirit: let us live this culture of peace every single day.\", \"from\": 8945, \"to\": 9059, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 8967, \"to\": 8975}, {\"ngram\": \"this Olympic spirit\", \"from\": 8987, \"to\": 9006}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 9012, \"to\": 9014}, {\"ngram\": \"this culture\", \"from\": 9020, \"to\": 9032}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 9036, \"to\": 9041}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There was also special praise for the 45,000 volunteers who assisted during the Games, which began with a rain-soaked opening ceremony along the Seine on 26 July.As well as reflecting on the Olympics in Paris, the closing ceremony provided a showcase for Los Angeles, which will host the Games for a third time in 2028.R&B artist H.E.R.\", \"from\": 9059, \"to\": 9396, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9205, \"end\": 9210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999601211823673, \"rank\": 3.987747989151786e-05, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 9263, \"end\": 9268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.556120703327853e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 9315, \"end\": 9326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.956721663598194e-14, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 9390, \"end\": 9396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H.E.R.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8298089014042313e-35, \"text\": \"H.E.R.\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H.E.R.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H.E.R.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"special praise\", \"from\": 9075, \"to\": 9089}, {\"ngram\": \"the 45,000 volunteers\", \"from\": 9094, \"to\": 9115}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 9136, \"to\": 9145}, {\"ngram\": \"a rain-soaked opening ceremony\", \"from\": 9164, \"to\": 9194}, {\"ngram\": \"26 July\", \"from\": 9214, \"to\": 9221}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 9247, \"to\": 9259}, {\"ngram\": \"the closing ceremony\", \"from\": 9270, \"to\": 9290}, {\"ngram\": \"a showcase\", \"from\": 9300, \"to\": 9310}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 9344, \"t