am\": \"Cruise\", \"from\": 20935, \"to\": 20941}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 20958, \"to\": 20963}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic rings\", \"from\": 21008, \"to\": 21021}, {\"ngram\": \"a special correspondent\", \"from\": 21065, \"to\": 21088}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 21132, \"to\": 21137}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 21174, \"to\": 21178}, {\"ngram\": \"a memorable finale\", \"from\": 21182, \"to\": 21200}, {\"ngram\": \"the appetite\", \"from\": 21214, \"to\": 21226}, {\"ngram\": \"four years' time.00votesArticle\", \"from\": 21231, \"to\": 21262}, {\"ngram\": \"his closing speech\", \"from\": 21273, \"to\": 21291}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"sensational\\\" Games\", \"from\": 21366, \"to\": 21387}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2024 Paralympics will be held in the French capital from 28 August to 8 September.The Olympic Games of a new era'Bach, who will step down as IOC president in 2025, said Paris 2024 had been \\\"sensational, or dare I say, 'Seine-sational'\\\" - a play on words referencing the river which flows through the host city.He added that they were \\\"Olympic Games of a new era\\\" as the first \\\"delivered completely under our Olympic agenda reforms: younger, more urban, more inclusive, more sustainable and the first Olympic Games with full gender parity\\\".The German praised athletes for their \\\"simply amazing\\\" performances, saying they showed \\\"what greatness we humans are capable of\\\".He continued: \\\"During all this time, you lived peacefully together under one roof in the Olympic Village.\", \"from\": 21391, \"to\": 22169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21432, \"end\": 21438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.5273597616931242, \"rank\": 0.6080213496216695, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 21536, \"end\": 21539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.5721310421439164e-35, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 21564, \"end\": 21574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4512950956881166e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 22153, \"end\": 22168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3056227608798627e-20, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 2024 Paralympics\", \"from\": 21391, \"to\": 21411}, {\"ngram\": \"28 August\", \"from\": 21452, \"to\": 21461}, {\"ngram\": \"8 September\", \"from\": 21465, \"to\": 21476}, {\"ngram\": \"The Olympic Games\", \"from\": 21477, \"to\": 21494}, {\"ngram\": \"a new era'Bach\", \"from\": 21498, \"to\": 21512}, {\"ngram\": \"- a play\", \"from\": 21631, \"to\": 21639}, {\"ngram\": \"words\", \"from\": 21643, \"to\": 21648}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 21661, \"to\": 21670}, {\"ngram\": \"the host city\", \"from\": 21691, \"to\": 21704}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Olympic Games\", \"from\": 21729, \"to\": 21743}, {\"ngram\": \"a new era\", \"from\": 21747, \"to\": 21756}, {\"ngram\": \"our Olympic agenda reforms\", \"from\": 21799, \"to\": 21825}, {\"ngram\": \"the first Olympic Games\", \"from\": 21885, \"to\": 21908}, {\"ngram\": \"full gender parity\\\"\", \"from\": 21914, \"to\": 21933}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 21953, \"to\": 21961}, {\"ngram\": \"their \\\"simply amazing\\\" performances\", \"from\": 21966, \"to\": 22001}, {\"ngram\": \"what greatness\", \"from\": 22023, \"to\": 22037}, {\"ngram\": \"we humans\", \"from\": 22038, \"to\": 22047}, {\"ngram\": \"all this time\", \"from\": 22086, \"to\": 22099}, {\"ngram\": \"one roof\", \"from\": 22137, \"to\": 22145}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You embraced each other.\", \"from\": 22170, \"to\": 22194, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You respected each other, even if your countries are divided by war and conflict.\", \"from\": 22195, \"to\": 22276, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your countries\", \"from\": 22229, \"to\": 22243}, {\"ngram\": \"war\", \"from\": 22259, \"to\": 22262}, {\"ngram\": \"conflict\", \"from\": 22267, \"to\": 22275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You created a culture of peace.\", \"from\": 22277, \"to\": 22308, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a culture\", \"from\": 22289, \"to\": 22298}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 22302, \"to\": 22307}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This inspired all of us and billions of people around the globe.\", \"from\": 22308, \"to\": 22373, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 22330, \"to\": 22332}, {\"ngram\": \"billions\", \"from\": 22337, \"to\": 22345}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 22349, \"to\": 22355}, {\"ngram\": \"the globe\", \"from\": 22363, \"to\": 22372}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you for making us dream.\", \"from\": 22374, \"to\": 22404, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 22395, \"to\": 22397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you for making us believe in a better world for everyone.\", \"from\": 22405, \"to\": 22468, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 22426, \"to\": 22428}, {\"ngram\": \"a better world\", \"from\": 22440, \"to\": 22454}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 22459, \"to\": 22467}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We know that the Olympic Games cannot create peace.\", \"from\": 22468, \"to\": 22520, \"entit