 Olympic agenda reforms: younger, more urban, more inclusive, more sustainable and the first Olympic Games with full gender parity\\\".The German praised athletes for their \\\"simply amazing\\\" performances, saying they showed \\\"what greatness we humans are capable of\\\".He continued: \\\"During all this time, you lived peacefully together under one roof in the Olympic Village.\", \"from\": 23801, \"to\": 24493, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23860, \"end\": 23863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.5721310421439164e-35, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 23888, \"end\": 23898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4512950956881166e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 24477, \"end\": 24492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3056227608798627e-20, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic Games\", \"from\": 23801, \"to\": 23818}, {\"ngram\": \"a new era'Bach\", \"from\": 23822, \"to\": 23836}, {\"ngram\": \"- a play\", \"from\": 23955, \"to\": 23963}, {\"ngram\": \"words\", \"from\": 23967, \"to\": 23972}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 23985, \"to\": 23994}, {\"ngram\": \"the host city\", \"from\": 24015, \"to\": 24028}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Olympic Games\", \"from\": 24053, \"to\": 24067}, {\"ngram\": \"a new era\", \"from\": 24071, \"to\": 24080}, {\"ngram\": \"our Olympic agenda reforms\", \"from\": 24123, \"to\": 24149}, {\"ngram\": \"the first Olympic Games\", \"from\": 24209, \"to\": 24232}, {\"ngram\": \"full gender parity\\\"\", \"from\": 24238, \"to\": 24257}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 24277, \"to\": 24285}, {\"ngram\": \"their \\\"simply amazing\\\" performances\", \"from\": 24290, \"to\": 24325}, {\"ngram\": \"what greatness\", \"from\": 24347, \"to\": 24361}, {\"ngram\": \"we humans\", \"from\": 24362, \"to\": 24371}, {\"ngram\": \"all this time\", \"from\": 24410, \"to\": 24423}, {\"ngram\": \"one roof\", \"from\": 24461, \"to\": 24469}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You embraced each other.\", \"from\": 24494, \"to\": 24518, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You respected each other, even if your countries are divided by war and conflict.\", \"from\": 24519, \"to\": 24600, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your countries\", \"from\": 24553, \"to\": 24567}, {\"ngram\": \"war\", \"from\": 24583, \"to\": 24586}, {\"ngram\": \"conflict\", \"from\": 24591, \"to\": 24599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You created a culture of peace.\", \"from\": 24601, \"to\": 24632, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a culture\", \"from\": 24613, \"to\": 24622}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 24626, \"to\": 24631}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This inspired all of us and billions of people around the globe.\", \"from\": 24632, \"to\": 24697, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 24654, \"to\": 24656}, {\"ngram\": \"billions\", \"from\": 24661, \"to\": 24669}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 24673, \"to\": 24679}, {\"ngram\": \"the globe\", \"from\": 24687, \"to\": 24696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you for making us dream.\", \"from\": 24698, \"to\": 24728, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 24719, \"to\": 24721}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you for making us believe in a better world for everyone.\", \"from\": 24729, \"to\": 24792, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 24750, \"to\": 24752}, {\"ngram\": \"a better world\", \"from\": 24764, \"to\": 24778}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 24783, \"to\": 24791}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We know that the Olympic Games cannot create peace.\", \"from\": 24792, \"to\": 24844, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 24806, \"to\": 24823}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 24838, \"to\": 24843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the Olympic Games can create a culture of peace that inspires the world.\", \"from\": 24845, \"to\": 24921, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 24849, \"to\": 24866}, {\"ngram\": \"a culture\", \"from\": 24878, \"to\": 24887}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 24891, \"to\": 24896}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 24911, \"to\": 24920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is why I call on everyone who shares this Olympic spirit: let us live this culture of peace every single day.\", \"from\": 24922, \"to\": 25036, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 24944, \"to\": 24952}, {\"ngram\": \"this Olympic spirit\", \"from\": 24964, \"to\": 24983}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 24989, \"to\": 24991}, {\"ngram\": \"this culture\", \"from\": 24997, \"to\": 25009}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 25013, \"to\": 25018}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There was also special praise for the 45,000 volunteers who assisted during the Games, which began with a rain-soaked opening ceremony along the Seine on 26 July.As well as reflecting on the Olympics in Paris, the closing ceremony provided a showcase for Los Angeles, which will host the Games for a third time in 2028.R&B artist H.E.R.\", \"from\": 25036, \"to\": 25373, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 25182, \"end\": 25187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999601211823673, \"rank\": 3.987747989151786e-05, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\"