er Eaton took the Olympic flag on a tour of the city - visiting sites such as the Los Angeles Memorial Coliseum and Venice Beach - while Cruise was pictured in front of the iconic Hollywood sign, complete with Olympic rings.Rapper Snoop Dogg, who has been working as a special correspondent for American television network NBC during Paris 2024, performed alongside Dr Dre as part of a memorable finale that whetted the appetite for four years' time.00votesArticle Rating The Olympic Games of a new era' Bach, who will step down as IOC president in 2025, said Paris 2024 had been \\\"sensational, or dare I say, 'Seine-sational'\\\" - a play on words referencing the river which flows through the host city.\", \"from\": 25374, \"to\": 26267, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 25388, \"end\": 25412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Star-Spangled_Banner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"American national anthem\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Star-Spangled_Banner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Star-Spangled_Banner\"}, {\"begin\": 25420, \"end\": 25435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 25489, \"end\": 25502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Courtney_(cyclist)\", \"score\": 0.9999981956923782, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kate Courtney\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Courtney_(cyclist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Courtney_(cyclist)\"}, {\"begin\": 25527, \"end\": 25542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"score\": 0.6562406956374156, \"rank\": 0.2753288987434648, \"text\": \"Michael Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q21